int.com/post/81596126766/see-chargepoint-on-newswatch-tv-we-met-with-the\n  | accessdate = 25 August 2014}}\n* {{Citation\n |title       = As Seen On NewsWatchTV: TheFind\u2019s patented search technology\n |date        = 30 September 2013\n |url         = http://merchantblog.thefind.com/2013/09/uncategorized/as-seen-on-newswatchtv-thefinds-patented-search-technology-in-its-ipad-app/\n |accessdate  = 22 August 2014\n |url-status     = dead\n |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20141007095650/http://merchantblog.thefind.com/2013/09/uncategorized/as-seen-on-newswatchtv-thefinds-patented-search-technology-in-its-ipad-app/\n |archivedate = 7 October 2014\n}}\n* {{Citation\n  | title = Bridge Communications: Parent Company of NewsWatch\n  | date = 12 October 2015\n  | url = http://bridgecomdc.newswatchtv.com/\n  | accessdate = 14 January 2016}}\n* {{Citation\n  | title = New GraphicAudio Access\u00ae Mobile Apps Featured On Newswatch TV\n  | date = 27 March 2014\n  | url = http://www.appsandsongs.com/appsandsongs/new-graphicaudio-access-mobile-apps-featured-newswatch-tv/\n  | accessdate = 18 August 2014}}\n* {{Citation\n  | title = Siemens Smart Hearing Aid Featured on NewsWatch Television\n  | date = 15 February 2015\n  | url = http://www.prweb.com/releases/2015/02/prweb12517927.htm\n  | accessdate = 15 December 2016}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{official website|http://www.newswatchtv.com/}}\n\n[[Category:1990 American television series debuts]]\n[[Category:1990s American television news programs]]\n[[Category:2000s American television news programs]]\n[[Category:2010s American television news programs]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:Ion Television original programming]]\n[[Category:Promotion and marketing communications]]\n", "text_old": "{{infobox television |\n  | show_name = NewsWatch\n  | image = NewsWatch Logo.png\n  | caption = \n  | runtime = 30 minutes\n  | starring = Andrew Tropeano (Host), Susan Bridges (Host), Michel